- id: 1468-table-of-contents-generator
  title: Table of contents generator
  tags:
  - writing
  - table
  - contents
  - generator
  family: writing
  body: 'Imagine that you are a professional editor who has been hired to create a
    table of contents for a new book. The author has provided you with a detailed
    summary of the book, which you can use to create a table of contents that accurately
    reflects the structure and content of the book. Your task is to generate a table
    of contents for the book with the following title and description : ''[PROMPT]''.
    Your table of contents should include at least five main sections, each with a
    descriptive title that accurately reflects the content of the section. The target
    language is [TARGETLANGUAGE].'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
